lead_paragraph: The Sports of The Times column on Tuesday, about a football scheduling dispute between Rutgers and Notre Dame, referred incorrectly to Air Force and Navy, which joined Rutgers and some private universities among the football leaders in a recent N.C.A.A. academic report. They are public institutions, not private.
